{"tid":1710164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天主教教區包庇賣主猶大(陳玉強)西灣河事件後續","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:25:08.000Z","uid":332160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56b20d67c61a7bfcb4534a71b88e7642564bba0b","tid":1710164,"uid":332160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EB6aaKP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEB6aaKP.png&h=6d62daf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSs4Zn5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSs4Zn5.png&h=e278fc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源<a href=\"https://catholic.org.hk/media-20191111/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcatholic.org.hk%2Fmedia-20191111%2F&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=ed62e11e\" target=\"_blank\">https://catholic.org.hk/media-20191111/</a><br />\nXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX<br />\n<br />\n教區就陳玉強放警入教堂抓捕一事的回應<br />\n其重點點句子:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事實上並非是陳執事容許警方進入聖堂範圍內。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這個很明顯的是與我們昨天在直播所見所聽的不符<br />\n陳玉強：<br />\n「希望警察可以帶佢哋5個人走，我哋冇權阻止佢哋（警察）入黎，<br />\n佢哋有權入嚟執法。希望大家平平安安出去」<br />\n<br />\n這是假見證,這是撒謊<br />\n撒謊人的父是誰?<br />\n絕對不會是&lt;天主經&gt;的第一句,我們的天父<br />\n撒謊者的父親是魔鬼 (若8:44)<br />\n教區何時已認魔鬼作父了?<br />\n心痛<br />\n<br />\n更諷刺的是與其聖十字架堂主任於此事後的公開信內容不符<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTYch6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTYch6d.jpg&h=01746e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當孩子們期望/以為聖堂是避難所時，<br />\n他們所體驗的卻是負賣所！<br />\n放警入聖堂，捉拿入來求助的平民百姓，<br />\n二五比廢佬更可恨<br />\n披着聖堂執事之名，￼沒有守護聖堂，沒有捨己為人。￼<br />\n教區竟然還在包庇此人<br />\n面對天主教教區的虛偽態度<br />\n及其於信中不再誠諾能有效保護手足<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">可惜，教堂已不像以往的時代，在今時今日，教堂無從保障進入其內的人士不被依法逮捕。</span></strong><br />\n這個曾經可作避難的私人地方<br />\n手足還要去避難嗎?<br />\n基督宗教尊嚴蕩然無存<br />\n天主教的求全對比伊斯蘭教嘅堅毅<br />\n使人不勝唏噓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料補充:<br />\n<br />\n陳玉強事後公開回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SLuLOTj_LCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSLuLOTj_LCs&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=8c70e9d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SLuLOTj_LCs</a><br />\n五位手足被捕後仍被暴力對待<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mm6ua0y7XlY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMm6ua0y7XlY&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=50119f28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mm6ua0y7XlY</a>"},{"pid":"c75612c6ed2cbfde5576cd201f09122414150105","tid":1710164,"uid":281972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d28ef6f2110ae90ed97518cd325eb021a836b5f","tid":1710164,"uid":64153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5a1a9e9e4f191661f4f890b6259b7e937033d8fe","tid":1710164,"uid":112622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bda8a4e695aa4dd59065724ebd1d38c3062af6c6","tid":1710164,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"佢呢D人要落地獄"},{"pid":"bb44e2ff7c321fd9cabb352f54d3c7fd02311aab","tid":1710164,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"005c1fb5a287e6866b341019f0f5ac43592f21ca","tid":1710164,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}